org.gvsig.rastertools.raw.tools
Class VRTFileCreator

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.rastertools.raw.tools.VRTFileCreator

public class VRTFileCreator
extends java.lang.Object

This class is user to create a VRT file. It writes the file when the "writeFile" method is called. If some params are not seted the deafult values will bi used.

Author:
Jorge Piera Llodrá (piera_jor@gva.es)
